%2C000%20from%20supporters%20through%20a%20newsletter%20callout.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ERead%20what%20they%20sent%20in%20that%20newsletter%2C%20and%20the%20pitch%20deck%20slides%20that%20convinced%20investors%20to%20buy%20in.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Matt%20Rum%20worked%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsquare-ecommerce-moves-upmarket-economic-uncertainty-block-2023-3%5C%22%3ESquare%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20developing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcash-app%5C%22%3ECash%20App%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20and%20his%20coworkers%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20golf%20on%20the%20weekends.%20They%20were%20all%20competitive%2C%20the%20former%20college%20basketball%20player%20said%2C%20so%20they%20started%20putting%20money%20on%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20keeping%20track%20of%20multiple%20games%20on%20paper%20scorecards%20and%20divvying%20up%20bets%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20became%20difficult.%20So%20Rum%20and%20his%20cofounder%2C%20Thomas%20Reinholm%2C%20built%20the%20initial%20prototype%20for%20the%20on-course%20betting%20platform%20that%20eventually%20became%20LoopGolf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Rum%20and%20Reinholm%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20turned%20LoopGolf%20from%20a%20weekend%20hobby%20into%20a%20company.%20They%20raised%20close%20to%20%242%20million%20through%20venture-capital%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20summer%20was%20the%20company's%20first%20season%20with%20its%20product%20in%20the%20App%20Store.%20Rum%20said%20LoopGolf%20acquired%20about%207%2C000%20customers%20and%20did%20about%20%24250%2C000%20in%20gross%20payment%20volume%2C%20meaning%20money%20flowing%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20betting%20platform.%20Customers%20can%20connect%20with%20friends%20to%20bet%20on%20rounds%20and%20transfer%20money%20in%20the%20app%2C%20and%20the%20product%20also%20has%20an%20on-course%20GPS%20using%20satellite%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it's%20time%20to%20play%2C%20users%20select%20the%20course%2C%20set%20the%20stakes%2C%20and%20invite%20their%20partners%20to%20join%20the%20match%20on%20the%20app.%20Players%20update%20their%20score%20throughout%20the%20round%2C%20and%20once%20it%20ends%2C%20the%20app%20instantly%20distributes%20funds%20between%20LoopGolf%20wallets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReally%20exciting%20first%20summer%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Rum%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BReally%20validating%20that%20it's%20not%20just%20us%20that%20have%20these%20problems%20and%20showcasing%20that%20the%20product%20is%20valuable%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20golfers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAppealing%20to%20a%20younger%20generation%20of%20golfers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20didn't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20spend%20on%20marketing%2C%20but%20it%20hired%20a%20young%20golfer%20to%20help%20make%20content%20for%20social%20media.%20He%20hadn't%20done%20this%20kind%20of%20work%20before%2C%20Rum%20said%2C%20but%20his%20creative%20videos%20found%20the%20right%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20kind%20of%20struck%20gold%2C%26quot%3B%20Rum%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe'd%20have%20a%20couple%20that%20have%20gone%20viral%2C%20and%20have%20acquired%204%2C000%20or%205%2C000%20customers%20via%20TikTok%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20videos%20have%20gotten%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20views%2C%20and%20the%20company%20now%20has%20almost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40loopgolfclub%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E7%2C000%20TikTok%20followers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20app's%20demographic%20is%20primarily%20ages%2021%20to%2035%2C%20Rum%20said.%20Part%20of%20that%20is%20because%20of%20TikTok%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20because%20older%20golfers%20are%20more%20resistant%20to%20changes%20in%20their%20golf%20game%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20way%20of%20doing%20things%20out%20on%20the%20golf%20course%20and%20they%20don't%20necessarily%20want%20to%20incorporate%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Rum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoopGolf%20recently%20added%20golf%20creator%20Mike%20Bartels%2C%20who%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpinsandpassports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%2012%2C000%20Instagram%20followers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20its%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERum%20said%20the%20multiplayer%20experience%20has%20also%20helped%20drive%20customers%20toward%20the%20app%20because%20users%20are%20incentivized%20to%20get%20their%20friends%20to%20sign%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20get%20the%20most%20value%20out%20of%20your%20app%2C%20you%20want%20your%20friends%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Rum%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20benefiting%20from%20that%20word-of-mouth%20marketing%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20sports%20betting%20operators%20have%20that%20same%20luxury.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGetting%20creative%20and%20scrappy%20with%20fundraising%20efforts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20quitting%20their%20jobs%20at%20Square%20in%202021%2C%20Rum%20and%20Reinholm%20fundraised%20about%20%242%20million%20from%20VCs%20to%20build%20their%20app.%20But%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-online-gambling-companies-raising-most-money-vc-funding-2023-8%5C%22%3Einvestments%20have%20slowed%20in%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20for%20sports%20gambling%20startups%20and%20high-risk%2C%20early-stage%20companies%2C%20LoopGolf%20needed%20to%20find%20another%20way%20to%20stay%20afloat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20striking%20out%20left%20and%20right%26quot%3B%20with%20VCs%2C%20Rum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20turned%20in%20August%20to%20the%20community%20they'd%20built%20through%20their%20weekly%20newsletter%2C%20The%20Sunday%20Sweat%2C%20offering%20the%20chance%20to%20be%20a%20stakeholder%20in%20the%20company.%20The%20effort%20raised%20about%20%2450%2C000%20to%20help%20fuel%20product%20development%20and%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%20fundraising%20message%20the%20team%20sent%20at%20the%20top%20of%20their%20newsletter%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe've%20been%20receiving%20a%20lot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0of%20interest%20lately%20from%20our%20community%20regarding%20how%20to%20invest%20in%20LoopGolf%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20take%20this%20opportunity%20to%20make%20an%20announcement.%20First%20off%2C%20we're%20greatly%20humbled%20by%20this%20level%20of%20interest%20and%20the%20thought%20of%20having%20a%20super%20engaged%20community%20with%20some%20skin%20in%20the%20game%20is%20greatly%20appealing%20to%20us.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EGiven%20that%20many%20of%20you%20are%20new%20here%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20we%20felt%20like%20it%20is%20a%20great%20time%20to%20share%20our%20full%20vision%20to%20build%20golf's%20first%20real%20money%20super%20app%20%E2%80%94%20where%20gaming%2C%20fintech%20and%20e-commerce%20intersect%20to%20create%20a%20one-stop%20shop%20for%20golfers.%20Here%20is%20our%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflight.beehiiv.net%2Fv2%2Fclicks%2FeyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..jj2rUYppl7vv51sz9M0iLyfYAxIY5ngtssYIMyyNHno%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evision%20deck%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20with%20that%20in%20mind%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0we're%20are%20wrapping%20up%20our%20first%20round%20of%20fundraising%20this%20month%20and%20have%20reserved%20the%20last%20%2450%2C000%20for%20you!%20We%20are%20giving%2050%20members%20the%20opportunity%20to%20invest%20a%20%241%2C000%20each%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month.%20If%20you%20or%20anyone%20you%20know%20is%20interested%20in%20having%20some%20skin%20in%20the%20game%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20Matt%20Rum%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflight.beehiiv.net%2Fv2%2Fclicks%2FeyJhb