s%20say%20they%20lack%2C%20survey%20finds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20walking%20at%20Google%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b1a87bf9a259001947689a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E70%25%20of%20Gen%20Z%20want%20to%20climb%20up%20the%20corporate%20ladder%20to%20the%20C-suite%2C%20an%20Adobe%20Survey%20found.%20%3Cp%3ETayfun%20Coskun%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20Adobe%20survey%20found%20that%20almost%20half%20of%20Gen%20Z%20workers%20want%20more%20training%20on%20hard%20skills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20only%20a%20third%20were%20keen%20on%20polishing%20up%20their%20soft%20skills%20like%20communication.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeanwhile%20firms%20like%20Deloitte%20and%20KPMG%20have%20been%20raising%20concerns%20about%20Gen%20Z's%20lack%20of%20workplace%20etiquette.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20have%20caught%20a%20bad%20reputation%20for%20having%20poor%20communication%20skills%20at%20work%20but%20they're%20more%20focused%20on%20amping%20up%20their%20technical%20prowess%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.adobe.com%2Fen%2Fpublish%2F2023%2F09%2F27%2Fadobe-future-workforce-study-what-us-employers-need-know-about-gen-z-workplace%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAdobe%20survey%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdobe's%20Future%20Workforce%20Study%20surveyed%20over%201%2C000%20Gen%20Z%20workers%20in%20the%20US%20in%20early%20September%20to%20explore%20their%20career%20motivations%20and%20workplace%20expectations.%20The%20respondents%20had%20been%20working%20full-time%20for%20a%20medium%20to%20large-sized%20company%20for%20up%20to%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERespondents%20were%20asked%20about%20the%20type%20of%20training%20they%20want%20more%20of%20at%20work.%20The%20survey%20found%20that%2048%25%20of%20Gen%20Z%20wanted%20more%20training%20on%20hard%20skills%20related%20to%20their%20job%20whilst%20only%20a%20third%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20build%20on%20their%20soft%20skills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Adobe%20said%20that%20respondents%20were%20given%20a%20definition%20for%20hard%20skills%20and%20soft%20skills.%20They%20were%20informed%20that%20hard%20skills%20refer%20to%20job-related%20or%20technical%20knowledge%20and%20abilities%2C%20while%20soft%20skills%20were%20classed%20as%20interpersonal%20skills%20and%20traits%20that%20shape%20how%20you%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20reflected%20in%20their%20attitudes%20towards%20AI%20with%20almost%20half%20saying%20they%20feel%20prepared%20for%20their%20employer%20to%20adopt%20the%20technology%20in%20everyday%20work.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdobe%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3Ehalf%20of%20the%20respondents%20admitted%20to%20having%20used%20the%20technology%20to%20aid%20their%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E70%25%20of%20Gen%20Z%20are%20eager%20to%20climb%20up%20the%20corporate%20ladder%20to%20the%20C-suite%20and%20grow%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20impact%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20Adobe's%20survey%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20Gen%20Z's%20perceptions%20of%20themselves%2C%20managers%20are%20more%20concerned%20about%20their%20lack%20of%20communication%20and%20interpersonal%20skills%20in%20the%20workplace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMajor%20companies%20including%20Deloitte%20and%20PWC%20have%20noted%20a%20deficiency%20in%20soft%20skills%20in%20pandemic-era%20graduates%20including%20teamwork%20and%20collaboration%2C%20this%20is%20often%20linked%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20most%20Gen%20Z%20workers%20had%20to%20study%20and%20work%20remotely%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fa8b20502-8238-4655-ba82-30d6243332d9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%20May.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20there%20is%20a%20greater%20need%20for%20employers%20to%20provide%20training%20on%20basic%20professional%20and%20working%20skills%2C%20that%20wasn't%20necessary%20in%20prior%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Jackie%20Henry%2C%20Deloitte's%20UK%20managing%20partner%20for%20people%20and%20purpose%2C%20told%20the%20FT.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20like%20KPMG%20and%20Protiviti%20are%20even%20teaching%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-taking-courses-send-emails-office-clothes-wsj-2023-6%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGen%20Z%20hires%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20to%20send%20emails%2C%20what%20to%20wear%20in%20the%20office%2C%20and%20how%20to%20maintain%20the%20appropriate%20level%20of%20eye%20contact%20during%20a%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-workers-want-more-training-hard-skills-survey-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696341478000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651bf1682ce014759e731b16%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-workers-want-more-training-hard-skills-survey-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adobe's%20new%20Future%20Workforce%20Study%20surveyed%201%2C000%20Gen%20Z%20workers%20and%20found%20that%2070%25%20are%20eager%20to%20climb%20the%20corporate%20ladder%20to%20the%20C-suite.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbhaimiya%40insider.com%20(Sawdah%20Bhaimiya)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-workers-want-more-training-hard-skills-survey-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BITS%20Pilani%20Engineers%E2%80%99%20Solar-Powered%20Home%20Saves%20Over%202%20Lakh%20Litres%20of%20Water%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Ashish%20Panda%20got%20married%20to%20his%20college%20sweetheart%20Madhulika%20whom%20he%20met%20at%20BITS%20Pilani%2C%20Rajasthan.%20Like%20any%20newly%20wedded%20couple%2C%20their%20forage%20for%20a%20sweet%20home%20started%20soon%20after.%20However%2C%20they%20did%20not%20want%20to%20live%20in%20conventional%20cement%20brick%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENative%20to%20Bhubaneswar%20and%20Vijayawada%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20settle%20thousands%20of%20kilometres%20away%20in%20rural%20Rajasthan%2C%20away%20from%20the%20hustle%20of%20metros.%20And%20there%2C%20they%20built%20their%20house%20from%20lime%20and%20stones%20instead%20of%20going%20for%20a%20concrete%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20foundation%20to%20the%20interiors%2C%20the%20couple%20utilised%20local%20materials%20like%20lime%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebalwada%3C%2Fem%3E%20(slate)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Eghughra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(phyllite)%20stones%2C%20giving%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F285477%2Fsustainable-homes-energy-efficient-zero-waste-cut-electricity-water-bills-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20distinct%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20cement%2C%20they%20used%20stone%20slabs%20for%20the%20steps%2C%20roof%2C%20and%20balcony%20of%20the%20house.%20Stones%20were%20also%20the%20primary%20building%20material%20for%20the%20walls%2C%20while%20lime%20was%20used%20for%20plastering%2C%20masonry%2C%20and%20the%20roof.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20their%20dream%20home%20came%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-3-1695994950.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20house%20is%20constructed%20in%20an%20area%20of%203%2C200%20square%20feet.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-3-1695994950.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-3-1695994950-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-3-1695994950-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-3-1695994950-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-3-1695994950-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331351%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20is%20constructed%20in%20an%20area%20of%203%2C200%20square%20feet.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20cosmopolitan%20cities%20to%20rural%20tranquility%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Madhulika%20(43)%20is%20a%20computer%20science%20graduate%2C%20Ashish%20(42)%20pursued%20civil%20engineering.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20they%20worked%20with%20several%20non-profit%20organisations%20when%20their%20interests%20shifted%20to%20rural%20development%2C%20social%2C%20and%20environmental%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMadhulika%2C%20who%20pursued%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20in%20telecommunications%20from%20the%20US%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20our%20marriage%2C%20we%20have%20lived%20in%20different%20cities%20and%20countries%20as%20well.%20But%20we%20had%20decided%20to%20settle%20in%20Rajasthan%20while%20we%20were%20still%20in%20college.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20settling%20in%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Dungarpur%20in%20South%20Rajasthan%2C%20they%20lived%20in%20several%20cities%20like%20Anantpur%2C%20Udaipur%2C%20Chittorgarh%2C%20Bhilwara%2C%20and%20a%20few%20villages.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20always%20lived%20in%20state%20capitals%2C%20so%20we%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20quiet%20place%20without%20traffic%20noise.%20We%20discovered%20this%20town%20to%20be%20peaceful%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashish%2C%20who%20currently%20works%20with%20an%20NGO%20Sambhaav%20Trust%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20the%20couple%20purchased%20the%20land%20and%20began%20researching%20ways%20to%20create%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F244161%2Fthese-10-eco-friendly-homes-will-inspire-you-to-live-sustainably%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmentally%20friendly%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20sustainable%20house.%20They%20spent%2010%20months%20on%20this%20research%2C%20during%20which%20they%20consulted%20with%20several%20architects%20and%20studied%20houses%20as%20old%20as%20150%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%201999%2C%20Ashish%20and%20Madhulika%20met%20while%20studying%20at%20BITS%20Pilani.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSustainable-house-4-1695994976-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331352%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%201999%2C%20Ashish%20and%20Madhulika%20met%20while%20studying%20at%20BITS%20Pilani.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20traditional%20materials%20used%20by%20the%20local%20people.%20We%20discovered%20that%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20old%20houses%2C%20palaces%2C%20and%20mansions%20were%20built%20with%20stone%20and%20lime.%20These%20structures%2C%20despite%20not%20using%20cement%20and%20steel%2C%20have%20endured%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20outperformed%20RCC-built%20homes%2C%20which%20often%20deteriorate%20in%20just%20a%20few%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20Ashish%20and%20Madhulika%20employed%20a%20traditional%20roof%20construction%20method.%20They%20mixed%20lime%2C%20jaggery%2C%20fenugreek%2C%20and%20ropes%20for%20this%20purpose.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20makes%20the%20roof%20cool%20and%20waterproof%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ashish.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConstructed%20in%20an%20area%20of%203%2C200%20square%20feet%2C%20the%20two-storey%20house%20features%20two%20covered%20verandahs%2C%20a%20dining%20area%2C%20an%20open%20verandah%2C%20three%20bedrooms%20with%20two%20attached%20washrooms%20and%20one%20common%20washroom%20on%20the%20ground%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20storeroom%2C%20a%20balcony%2C%20a%20covered%20verandah%2C%20an%20open%20terrace%2C%20and%20a%20bedroom%20with%20an%20attached%20pantry%20and%20washroom.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20property%20includes%20a%20parking%20area%20with%20recharge%20pits%2C%20a%20black%20water%20treatment%20tank%2C%20and%20a%20grey%20water%20treatment%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20after%2016%20months%20of%20construction%2C%20the%20couple%20finally%20moved%20into%20their%20home%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%