Fa%3E%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20October%203%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20anti-terror%20case%20were%20questioned%20if%20they%20had%20reported%20on%20matters%20like%20the%202020%20Delhi%20riots%2C%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20against%20the%20three%20Central%20laws%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20journalists%20and%20commentators%20associated%20with%20the%20online%20news%20portal%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20taken%20to%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20special%20cell%20for%20questioning.%20The%20residences%20of%20many%20others%20were%20raided%2C%20and%20the%20police%20seized%20devices%20such%20as%20laptops%20and%20phones%20without%20providing%20a%20hash%20value%20%E2%80%93%20which%20defines%20how%20much%20data%20was%20on%20the%20device%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20seizure%20and%20can%20reveal%20any%20tampering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVeteran%20journalist%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%2C%20who%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20special%20cell%E2%80%99s%20office%20at%20around%208%20am%20and%20released%20around%206%20pm%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20revealed%20the%20bizarre%20line%20of%20questioning%20that%20the%20police%20adopted.%20He%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20called%20a%20US%20number%20which%20belongs%20to%20his%20brother-in-law%20and%20if%20he%20uses%20the%20Signal%20messaging%20app.%20He%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20had%20covered%20the%20Delhi%20riots%20and%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20happened%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20They%20may%20call%20me%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Guha%20Thakurta%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20his%20investigative%20reportage%20into%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20financial%20fraud%20and%20several%20other%20such%20reports%20on%20extant%20crony%20capitalism%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20officials%20asked%20me%20whether%20he%20covered%20Delhi%20riots.%20%E2%80%9CI%20said%20no%20but%20then%20they%20asked%20me%20whether%20I%20reported%20on%20farmers%20protests.%20I%20said%20yes.%20There%20were%20many%20people%20questioning%20me.%20All%20of%20them%20asked%20different%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FRvbaXcwzcMw%3Fsi%3DscLZpK5joAKd2EZ5%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20journalist%20who%20freelances%20for%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20a%20six%20member%20team%20comprising%20at%20least%20one%20inspector%20rank%20official%20of%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20special%20cell%20landed%20at%20the%20house%20with%20search%20notices%20that%20mentioned%20sections%20of%20the%20draconian%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA).%20%E2%80%9CThey%20already%20had%20all%20my%20information%20%E2%80%93%20my%20phone%20number%2C%20my%20address%2C%20and%20my%20online%20activity.%20They%20remained%20polite%20but%20persistently%20questioned%20me%20about%20my%20association%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20told%20them%20about%20the%20work%20that%20I%20do%20for%20the%20news%20portal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20kept%20asking%20me%20about%20my%20reports%20on%20the%20Delhi%20riots%2C%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%2C%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20journalist%20said%2C%20wishing%20not%20to%20be%20named.%20Most%20of%20the%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20reports%20on%20these%20issues%20highlighted%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures%20and%20missteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20still%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20are%20the%20charges%20against%20me%2C%20if%20there%20are%20any.%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20received%20any%20FIR.%20But%20they%20took%20away%20my%20phone%20and%20laptop.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20raided%20the%20journalists%E2%80%99%20house%20for%20over%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20junior%20member%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20editorial%20team%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fexplained-what-are-the-stories-done-by-journalists-raided-by-the-delhi-police-today%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20was%20asked%20if%20she%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpaid%20extra%E2%80%9D%20for%20stories%20on%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20and%20the%20Delhi%20riots.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20wanted%20to%20know%20why%20I%20wrote%20stories%20against%20the%20country%20and%20government.%20They%20had%20no%20follow%20up%20questions%2C%20just%20a%20performa%20that%20they%20were%20reading%20from%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20employee%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20surprised%20when%20the%20police%20arrived%20at%20her%20home%20at%206%20am%20and%20raided%20the%20place%20for%20three%20hours.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20taking%20away%20my%20electronic%20devices%20and%20my%20passport%2C%20they%20told%20me%2096%20places%20have%20been%20raided%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20against%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20apparently%20based%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20that%20says%20the%20portal%20received%20funding%20from%20an%20American%20millionaire%20who%20has%20furthered%20Chinese%20talking%20points.%20The%20NYT%20report%20was%20highlighted%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20who%20claimed%20that%20the%20portal%20and%20Congress%20leaders%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20received%20funds%20from%20China%20to%20create%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%20atmosphere%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20what%20charges%20have%20been%20levelled%20against%20the%20individuals%20who%20were%20raided%20or%20questioned.%20The%20search%20notice%20used%20by%20the%20police%20on%20Tuesday%20list%20charges%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20UAPA%2C%20conspiracy%20(section%20120%20B%2C%20IPC)%20and%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20(153%20A).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696341282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03191722%2Fnewsclick.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-raids-journos-questioned-delhi-riots-farmers-protest-covid-crisis%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Veteran%20journalist%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%20said%20he%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20called%20a%20US%20number%20which%20belongs%20to%20his%20brother-in-law%20and%20if%20he%20uses%20the%20Signal%20messaging%20app.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-raids-journos-questioned-delhi-riots-farmers-protest-covid-crisis%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22APOS%3A%20Fast-Evolving%20Sports%20to%20Remain%20the%20Unchanging%20Anchor%20of%20Media%20Biz%2C%20While%20Fans%20Drive%20Expansion%20in%20Asia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696341224000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2FIndia-Cricket.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235743211%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20more%20things%20change%2C%20the%20more%20things%20stay%20the%20same%2C%20appeared%20to%20be%20the%20proposition%20of%20two%20Wall%20Street%20insiders%20on%20the%20current%20entertainment%20landscape%20and%20the%20inviolable%20position%20of%20sports%20within%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20tough%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20intoned%20Joe%20Ravitch%20founder%20and%20partner%20of%20media%20focused%20investment%20firm%20Raine%2C%20speaking%20last%20week%20at%20the%20APOS%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C