%99s%20population%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%20over%2031%20lakh%20families%2C%20is%20living%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%20(BPL).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Foct%2F03%2Fin-gujarat-poverty-on-rise-count-of-families-using-bpl-cards-goes-up-2620399.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20BPL%20threshold%20is%20set%20at%20Rs%20816%20per%20capita%20per%20month%20for%20rural%20areas%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20for%20urban%20areas%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20Rs%2032%20per%20day%20for%20rural%20residents%20and%20Rs%2026%20for%20urban%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20state%20minister%20for%20rural%20development%20Bachubhai%20Maganbhai%20Khabad%2C%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20from%20Congress%20MLA%20Tushar%20Chaudhary%20on%20September%2014%2C%20there%20are%20a%20total%20of%2031%2C61%2C310%20BPL%20families%20identified%20in%20Gujarat.%20Among%20them%2C%2016%2C28%2C744%20families%20are%20classified%20as%20extremely%20poor%2C%20while%2015%2C32%2C566%20are%20categorised%20as%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20data%20indicates%20that%20the%20number%20of%20families%20in%20the%20BPL%20category%20has%20been%20increasing%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202020-21%2C%201%2C047%20families%20fell%20into%20the%20BPL%20category%2C%20with%20only%2014%20families%20managing%20to%20move%20out%20of%20it.%20In%202021-22%2C%201%2C751%20new%20families%20were%20added%20to%20the%20BPL%20category%2C%20and%20only%20two%20families%20improved%20their%20status.%20In%202022-23%2C%20the%20BPL%20category%20saw%20an%20increase%20of%20303%20families%2C%20with%20just%20one%20family%20escaping%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEconomist%20Hemant%20Kumar%20Shah%2C%20based%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20%E2%80%9Cif%20we%20assume%20an%20average%20of%20six%20members%20per%20poor%20family%20among%20the%2031.64%20lakh%20poor%20families%2C%20it%20implies%20that%20the%20BPL%20population%20in%20Gujarat%20totals%201%20crore%2089%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20indicating%20that%20approximately%20one-third%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%20is%20living%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696340666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F2824052844_aa09eee89b_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-third-of-gujarats-population-is-living-below-the-poverty-line-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202020-21%2C%201%2C047%20families%20fell%20into%20the%20BPL%20category%2C%20with%20only%2014%20families%20managing%20to%20move%20out%20of%20it.%20In%202022-23%2C%20the%20BPL%20category%20saw%20an%20increase%20of%20303%20families%2C%20with%20just%20one%20family%20escaping%20poverty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-third-of-gujarats-population-is-living-below-the-poverty-line-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98My%20Family%20Refused%20to%20Vaccinate%20Me%20Against%20Polio%3B%20I%20Was%2010-Month-Old%20When%20I%20Stopped%20Walking%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20assassinated%20on%2031%20October%201984%2C%20the%20news%20sparked%20riots%20across%20India%20soon%20after.%20The%20night%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20many%20innocent%20families%2C%20including%20that%20of%20a%2010-month-old%20baby%2C%20Shravan%20Chaudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConfined%20in%20his%20village%20home%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20he%20had%20a%20fever%20so%20high%20that%20it%20could%20not%20be%20measured%20on%20any%20instrument.%20And%20due%20to%20the%20nationwide%20strike%2C%20his%20family%20could%20not%20take%20him%20to%20the%20nearest%20hospital%20which%20was%2020%20km%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20ni