%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20that%20AI%20is%20helping%20eliminate%20some%20of%20the%20more%20tedious%20tasks%20of%20the%20workday%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20some%20jobs%20will%20likely%20be%20entirely%20replaced%20by%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20children%20will%20live%20to%20100%20and%20not%20have%20cancer%20because%20of%20technology%20and%20they'll%20probably%20be%20working%20three%20and%20a%20half%20days%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20Dimon%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Dimon%20believes%20that%2C%20despite%20some%20roles%20becoming%20obsolete%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20boosted%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20workers.%20Perhaps%20shaving%20off%20a%20day%20and%20a%20half%20of%20work%20will%20allow%20for%20more%20leisure%20time.%20It'll%20also%20impact%20the%20finance%20industry%2C%20affecting%20all%20aspects%20of%20workflow%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20process%2C%20so%2C%20errors%2C%20trading%2C%20hedging%2C%20research%2C%20every%20app%20every%20database%2C%20you%20could%20be%20applying%20AI.%20So%20it%20might%20be%20as%20a%20co-pilot%2C%20it%20might%20be%20to%20replace%20humans%2C%26quot%3B%20Dimon%20told%20Bloomberg.%20But%20he%20also%20assured%20that%20JPMorgan%20would%20%26quot%3Bredeploy%26quot%3B%20anyone%20whose%20job%20is%20replaced%20by%20AI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDimon%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20his%20prediction.%20Many%20economists%20believe%20that%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-chatgpt-ai-make-4-day-workweek-possible-in-future-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erise%20of%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20four-day%20workweek%20is%20more%20plausible.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-chatgpt-at-work-job-save-time-ai-2023-2%23use-it-to-a