di%3C%2Fa%3E%20claimed%20Tuesday%20while%20campaigning%20for%20the%20Assembly%20election%20due%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20dramatic%20fashion%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20declared%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20or%20KCR%20as%20he%20is%20known%2C%20and%20his%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20made%20multiple%20attempts%20to%20join%20the%20NDA.%20These%20were%20personally%20rebuffed%2C%20the%20PM%20told%20a%20cheering%20crowd.%20%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'we%20won't%20cheat%20people%20of%20Telangana.%20After%20that%20his%20mind%20was%20rattled.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20-%20whose%20BJP%20won%20a%20solitary%20seat%20in%20the%202018%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Ftelangana%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelangana%3C%2Fa%3E%20election%20and%20is%20without%20a%20government%20in%20South%20India%20-%20said%20his%20refusal%20angered%20and%20%26quot%3Bchanged%26quot%3B%20KCR%2C%20whom%20he%20also%20accused%20of%20corruption%20and%20nepotism%20in%20an%20all-out%20attack%20in%20Nizamabad%2C%20about%20180%20km%20from%20state%20capital%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20going%20to%20tell%20you%20a%20secret...%20100%20per%20cent%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20began%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20municipal%20elections%20happened%20(in%202020)%2C%20nobody%20got%20a%20majority.%20BJP%20won%2048%20seats...%20KCR%20needed%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-months-before-telangana-polls-bjps-big-change-suggests-a-reset-4179983%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E6%20Months%20Before%20Telangana%20Polls%2C%20BJP's%20Big%20Change%20Suggests%20A%20Reset%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKCR%20showered%20me%20with%20love...%20gave%20me%20a%20shawl.%20This%20was%20not%20in%20KCR's%20character.%20And%20then%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20include%20him%20in%20NDA.%20'You%20help%20us%20in%20Hyderabad%20municipality%20(election)'%2C%20he%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20refused...%20told%20him%20we%20won't%20cheat%20of%20people%20of%20Telangana%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%202020%20Hyderabad%20civic%20poll%20was%20a%20significant%20step%20forward%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20struggled%20for%20traction%20in%20the%20state%20till%20then.%20Of%20the%20150%20wards%2C%20KCR's%20party%20won%20just%2056%20-%20down%20from%2099%20in%20the%20previous%20election.%20The%20BRS'%20loss%20was%20the%20BJP's%20gain%2C%20which%20upped%20its%20tally%20from%20four%20to%2048.%C2%A0Eventually%20the%20BRS%20formed%20the%20city's%20government%20after%20last-minute%20support%20from%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi's%20AIMIM%2C%20which%20won%2044%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20flopped%2C%20winning%20just%20two%20wards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20BRS)%20got%20angry%20(after%20being%20refused%20entry%20to%20the%20NDA).%20But%20then%20he%20(KCR)%20came%20back...%20told%20me%20he%20now%20wants%20to%20give%20all%20responsibility%20to%20KTR%20(KT%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20his%20son%20and%20a%20Telangana%20minister).%20'I%20will%20send%20KTR%2C%20you%20please%20bless%20him'%2C%20KCR%20told%20me...%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelangana-minister-responds-to-pm-modis-family-run-party-swipe-at-kcr-4441313%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Minister%20Responds%20To%20PM%20Modi's%20%26quot%3BFamily-Run%20Party%26quot%3B%20Swipe%20At%20KCR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20then%20claimed%20he%20had%20severely%20scolded%20the%20Telangana%20leader.%20%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'KCR%2C%20this%20is%20democracy.%20Who%20are%20you%20to%20give%20KTR%20everything%3F%20Are%20you%20a%20king%3F'%20After%20that%20he%20never%20came%20before%20me.%20He%20is%20unable%20to%20face%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20