0his%20brother%20Prabhat%20Gupta%20in%202000%2C%20Satnam%20is%20the%20father%20of%20Lovepreet%20Singh%2C%20one%20of%20the%20four%20protesting%20farmers%20who%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Flakhimpur-kheri-speeding-car-linked-to-bjp-mla-collides-with-bike-killing-2%5C%22%3Emowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20death%20allegedly%20by%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20son%20Ashish%20Mishra%20%E2%80%98Monu%E2%80%99%20and%20his%20friends%20on%20October%203%2C%202021.%20Both%20incidents%20happened%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Flakhimpur-kheri-violence-was-a-long-time-coming%5C%22%3ETikonia%20area%20of%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20sugarcane-rich%20district%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20bordering%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20in%20May%20acquitted%20Teni%20in%20the%20Prabhat%20Gupta%20murder%20case%2C%20his%20brother%20Rajeev%2C%20who%20has%20been%20fighting%20for%20justice%20since%202000%2C%20recently%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20where%20he%20filed%20a%20special%20leave%20petition.%20The%20Tikonia%20case%20of%202021%2C%20in%20which%20eight%20persons%20were%20killed%20in%20total%20%E2%80%93%20four%20farmers%2C%20one%20journalist%2C%20two%20BJP%20workers%20and%20their%20driver%20%E2%80%93%20drags%20on%20in%20a%20trial%20court%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%20Monu%2C%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20is%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20four%20farmers%20and%20the%20journalist.%20The%20aggrieved%20families%20as%20well%20as%20farmer%20groups%20constantly%20demanded%2C%20though%20without%20success%2C%20that%20Teni%2C%20who%20gave%20a%20provocative%20speech%20against%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20October%203%2C%202021%20incident%2C%20be%20booked%20for%20criminal%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20Satnam%20Singh%20is%20yet%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20brutal%20death.%20Three%20vehicles%20belonging%20to%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20convoy%20ran%20over%20protesting%20farmers%2C%20killing%20Lovepreet%20and%20three%20other%20farmers.%20He%20acknowledges%20that%20the%20legal%20battle%20is%20tough%20as%20they%20are%20faced%20against%20an%20influential%20opponent%2C%20currently%20enjoying%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20positions%20in%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20law%20for%20them.%20The%20law%20is%20only%20for%20%3Cem%3Echote%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Elog%20%3C%2Fem%3E(small%20people).%20Even%20if%20they%20have%2050%20murders%20on%20their%20hands%2C%20nothing%20will%20happen%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20is%20willing%20to%20run%20the%20distance%2C%20that%20our%20legal%20system%20often%20asks%20of%20victims%2C%20for%20justice.%20%E2%80%9CTill%20we%20are%20alive%2C%20this%20struggle%20will%20go%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Sikh%20community%2C%20to%20which%20Satnam%20belongs%20to%2C%20own%20and%20farm%20large%20tracts%20of%20land%20in%20Kheri%20and%20adjoining%20districts%20of%20Pilibhit%2C%20Bahraich%20and%20Bareilly.%20They%20were%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20farmer%20protests%20against%20the%20three%20farm%20bills%20introduced%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20in%20the%20Terai%20region%20of%20UP.%20Satnam%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Palia%20area%20of%20Kheri%2C%20has%20two%20daughters.%20Lovepreet%2C%20his%20only%20son%2C%20aspired%20to%20go%20abroad%20to%20Australia%2C%20when%20the%20Tikonia%20tragedy%20cut%20short%20his%20dreams%20and%20life.%20He%20was%20barely%2020.%20While%20Satnam%20and%20other%20aggrieved%20families%20received%20Rs%2045%20lakh%20ex-gratia%20compensation%20they%20were%20promised%20by%20the%20government%2C%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20government%20job%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20fulfilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Flakhimpur-kheri-tells-us-its-time-to-rescue-a-democracy-in-retreat%5C%22%3ELakhimpur%