d%20his%20opposition%20to%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20on%20the%20day%20when%20the%20Bihar%20government%20released%20the%20results%20of%20its%20recently-concluded%20caste%20census%2C%20comprehensively%20outlining%20data%20on%20the%20caste%20make-up%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20should%20one%20consider%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statement%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20official%20position%20on%20caste%20census%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20assume%20so%20because%20a%20range%20of%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20pedalled%20different%20views%20on%20it.%20Senior%20leader%20and%20Union%20minister%20Giriraj%20Singh%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.abplive.com%2Fstates%2Fbihar-caste-census-report-cm-nitish-congratulates-survey-team-giriraj-singh-calls-it-just-an-eye-wash-lalu-prasad-yadav-1633279%5C%22%3Emislead%3C%2Fa%3E%20people%20through%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20while%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20senior-most%20saffron%20leader%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20has%20said%20that%20the%20process%20of%20counting%20caste%20groups%20in%20Bihar%20was%20actually%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20doing%20when%20the%20party%20was%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20ally%20in%20the%20state%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Bihar%20unit%20president%20Samrat%20Choudhary%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20exercised%20some%20restraint%20and%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20take%20a%20position%20only%20after%20studying%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmethodology%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20census%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20light%20of%20such%20contradictory%20remarks%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20saffron%20camp%2C%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20assume%20that%20the%20BJP%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20formulate%20a%20clear%20position%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20pan-India%20caste%20census%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20which%20the%20opposition%20parties%20have%20been%20consistently%20raising.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20clear%20to%20see%20that%20BJP%20is%20in%20a%20catch%2022%20situation.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20since%202014%20has%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20non-dominant%20Other%20Backward%20Class%20and%20Dalit%20communities%20and%20bring%20them%20into%20the%20Hindutva%20tent.%20Occasional%20representatives%20belonging%20to%20these%20communities%20were%20nominated%20for%20top%20posts%2C%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20gain%20their%20communities%E2%80%99%20confidence.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20also%20canvassed%20against%20agrarian%20caste%20groups%20like%20Yadavs%2C%20Marathas%2C%20and%20Jats%20and%20pitched%20them%20against%20non-dominant%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20fairly%20successful%20in%20fragmenting%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20communities%20as%20separate%20political%20groups.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20non-Yadav%20OBC%20and%20non-Jatav%20Dalits%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20were%20told%20by%20the%20BJP%20that%20most%20gains%20from%20Mandal-based%20affirmative%20action%20had%20been%20cornered%20by%20Yadavs.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20too%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20partially%20successful%20in%20mobilising%20small%20caste-based%20communities%20like%20Kalwar%2C%20Dhobi%2C%20Sonar%2C%20Bania%20and%20others%20against%20Yadavs.%20The%20saffron%20party%20allied%20with%20single-caste%20parties%2C%20largely%20led%20by%20one%20or%20other%20non-dominant%20OBC%20groups%20which%20advocated%20greater%20political%20power%20for%20their%20communities.%20These%20parties%2C%20like%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20Sanjay%20Nishad%E2%80%99s%20NISHAD%20party%2C%20Mukesh%20Sahni%E2%80%99s%20Vikassheel%20Insaan%20Party%2C%20or%20Anupriya%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20Apna%20Dal%20%E2%80%93%20even%20when%20they%20have%20been%20in%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20strongly%20supporting%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20or%20policies%20which%20may%20increase%20their%20share%20in%20political%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihars-caste-census-nitish%5C%22%3EBihar%E2%80%99s%20Caste%20Census%20Is%20a%20Bold%20Move%20Sure%20to%20Have%20Implications%20Beyond%20the%20State%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20consolidation%20of%20such%20groups%20by%20the%20BJP%20was%20also%20combined%20with%20a%20parallel%20process%20of%20alienating%20these%20groups%20from%20Muslims%20through%20a%20shrill%20communal%20rhetoric.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20non-dominant%20communities%20were%20given%20to%20understand%20that%20it%20was%20not%20only%20dominant%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits%20like%20Yadavs%20and%20Jatavs%20who%20were%20responsible%20for%20their%20under-representation%20but%20also%20Muslims%20whose%20tactical%20support%20was%20necessary%20for%20social%20justice%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20or%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20to%20come%20to%20power.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20Muslim-Yadav%20combination%2C%20the%20mainstay%20of%20parties%20like%20SP%20and%20RJD%20which%20are%20also%20the%20most%20vocal%20opponents%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%2C%20disintegrated%20under%20the%20expansive%20Hindutva%20umbrella.%20While%20BJP%20registered%20successive%20victories%20in%20northern%20India%20by%20riding%20on%20the%20newly-found%20support%20of%20under-represented%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20groups%2C%20the%20Mandal-based%20parties%20faced%20one%20loss%20after%20another.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20could%20successfully%20exploit%20the%20chink%20in%20the%20armour%20of%20social%20justice%20parties%20which%20in%20the%201990s%20and%20early%202000s%20had%20stemmed%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20growth.%20By%20doubling%20down%20on%20this%20political%20strategy%2C%20Modi%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20did%20not%20miss%20even%20a%20single%20chance%20to%20break%20apart%20the%20Mandal%20parties%20that%20had%20until%20now%20carried%20social%20justice%20political%20rhetoric%20on%20their%20shoulders.%20If%20the%20Adityanath-led%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20constituted%20a%20social%20justice%20commission%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20presence%20of%20non-dominant%20groups%2C%20the%20Modi-led%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fas-justice-rohini-panel-submits-report-will-the-modi-govt-move-ahead-with-sub-quotas-for-obcs%5C%22%3Eformed%20the%20Justice%20G.%20Rohini%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20explore%20the%20possibility%20of%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBC%20groups.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20these%20reports%20have%20been%20released.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20such%20moves%20were%20clearly%20drawn%20from%20the%20social%20justice%20template%20%E2%80%93%20taking%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20tactical%20decisions%20earlier%20to%20create%20EBC%20and%20Mahadalit%20categories%20in%20Bihar%20which%20helped%20him%20combat%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%E2%80%99s%20formidable%20Yadav-Muslim%20social%20coalition%20in%20the%20first%20decade%20of%20the%20millennium.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reluctance%20to%20implement%20the%20recommendations%20of%20these%20committees%20allowed%20the%20social%20justice%20parties%20to%20send%20a%20message%20that%20these%20commissions%20were%20formed%20as%20a%20ploy%20%E2%80%93%20to%20alienate%20agrarian%20caste%20groups%20further%20and%20weaken%20social%20justice%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20rather%20than%20to%20give%20the%20non-dominant%20OBC%20and%20Dalits%20groups%20their%20due%20share%20in%20power.%20Emboldening%20Hindutva%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20critics%20said%2C%20was%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20primary%20goal%2C%20not%20social%20justice%20because%20of%20which%20many%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20groups%20have%20veered%20towards%20the%20saffron%20party.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocialist%20parties%20like%20the%20RJD%2C%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20subsequently%20saw%20a%20window%20to%20intensify%20the%20rhetoric%20of%20social%20justice%20in%20such%20circumstances%2C%20and%20made%20the%20caste%20census%20their%20political%20plank.%20They%20argued%20that%20welfare%20measures%20could%20be%20better%20streamlined%20if%20the%20government%20knew%20the%20population%20and%20socio-economic%20indices%20of%20different%20communities%20in%20India.%20By%20demanding%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20the%20social%20justice%20parties%20acknowledged%20their%20past%20mistakes%20of%20prioritising%20dominant%20OBC%20groups%20over%20others.%20But%20the%20caste%20census%20also%20allowed%20them%20to%20see%20a%20democratic%20future%20for%20Lohiaite%20politics%20based%20on%20principles%20of%20equality%20and%20proportional%20representation%20of%20under-privileged%20communities.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhy-the-bjp-is-afraid-of-a-caste-census%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20BJP%20Is%20Afraid%20of%20a%20Caste%20Census%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20wishy-washy%20approach%20towards%20a%20caste%20census%20shows%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20confusion.%20First%2C%20it%20opposed%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202021%2C%20citing%20administrative%20and%20logistical%20reasons.%20More%20recently%2C%20the%20Centre%20argued%20in%20the%20apex%20court%20that%20only%20the%20Centre%20itself%20could%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20as%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9CUnion%20subject%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20prevent%20states%20like%20Bihar%2C%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand%20from%20conducting%20their%20own%20caste%20census.%20However%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fbihar-caste-survey-case-state-govt-census-centre-tells-supreme-court-236420%5C%22%3Ewithdrew%20the%20affidavit%20almost%20immediately%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20that%20the%20line%20of%20argument%20was%20inadvertently%20introduced%20in%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20introduced%20the%20Economically%20Weaker%20Section%20reservation%2C%20which%20effectively%20gives%20a%2010%25%20quota%20to%20only%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20individuals%20whose%20annual%20income%20is%20less%20than%20Rs%208%20lakhs.%20It%20meant%20that%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20groups%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Funcategorised%2Fbihar-caste-census-released-at-63-obc-ebc-groups-set-to-take-pole-position-in-state-politics%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPatna%253A%2520The%2520Bihar%2520government%2520finally%2C(EBC)%2520is%252026.01%2525.%5C%22%3Ewhich%20are%20a%20minority%20in%20the%20population%2C%20as%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20clearly%20reveals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20get%20a%20disproportionately%20higher%20share%20in%20the%20reservation%20system.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20move%20further%20muddied%20the%20waters.%20For%20instance%2C%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20groups%20in%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20or%20even%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20they%20constitute%20less%20than%205%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%20are%20entitled%20to%20a%2010%25%20reservation.%20Even%20in%20states%20like%20Bihar%20where%20they%20form%20a%20little%20over%2015%25%2C%20the%20EWS%20reservation%20allows%20them%20to%20get%20a%2010%25%20quota.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20OBC%20groups%20put%20together%20in%20Bihar%20form%20over%2063%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%20but%20can%20have%20only%2027%25%20reservation%20in%20government%20institutions.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20the%20PM%20has%20made%20a%20direct%20political%20statement%2C%20tacitly%20opposing%20caste%20census%2C%20but%20overlooking%20the%20multiple%20attempts%20by%20his%20own%20and%20other%20BJP-led%20state%20governments%20to%20devise%20ways%20for%20a%20caste%20count%20through%20various%20committees%20and%20policies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20was%20propelled%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20fragment%20social%20justice%20parties%20for%20electoral%20gains.%20And%2C%20now%20that%20such%20politicking%20has%20allowed%20the%20opposition%20to%20give%20it%20an%20ideological%20shape%20and%20direction%2C%20the%20BJP%20finds%20itself%20scratching%20its%20head.%20Mandal%20politics%20successfully%20prevented%20Hindutva%20ideology%20from%20taking%20deep%20roots%20in%20India%20earlier.%20It%20took%20an%20OBC%20leader%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20to%20assimilate%20aspects%20of%20that%20ideology%20to%20give%20Hindutva%20a%20subaltern%20colour%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%20The%20demand%20for%20a%20pan-India%20caste%20census%20is%20a%20concrete%20attempt%20by%20social%20justice%20parties%20to%20reclaim%20their%20roots%20in%20Indian%20politics.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMandal%20politics%20began%20in%20the%201980s%20with%20a%20demand%20for%20OBC%20quota%20but%20is%20now%20claiming%20proportional%20representation%20in%20power%20corridors%2C%20something%20that%20the%20social%20justice%20parties%20have%20been%20calling%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ehissedari%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20based%20on%20the%20famous%20Kanshi%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJinki%20jitni%20sankhya%20bhaari%2C%20utni%20unki%20hissedari%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20Translated%2C%20it%20means%2C%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20greater%20a%20community%E2%80%99s%20numbers%2C%20the%20greater%20its%20political%20representation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20caste%20census%20is%20truly%20a%20historic%20turn%20in%20the%20social%20justice%20movement%20of%20India.%20A%20Mandal%202.0%20moment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696330986000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F17103022%2FModi-Shah.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-narendra-modi-social-justice-caste-census-obc-dalit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20though%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20accused%20opposition%20parties%20of%20dividing%20the%20country%20along%20caste%20lines%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20denied%20that%20BJP's%20success%20in%20exploiting%20the%20chink%20in%20the%20armour%20of%20social%20justice%20parties%20has%20now%20come%20to%20affect%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-narendra-modi-social-justice-caste-census-obc-dalit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anurag%20Kashyap%20is%20delighted%20by%20Jawan's%20success%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696330929000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104132018%2Cimgsize-28812.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanurag-kashyap-is-delighted-by-jawans-box-office-success-plans-to-watch-and-review-the-srk-starrer-soon%2Farticleshow%2F104132023.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104132023.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Atlee's%20film%20'Jawan'%20has%20been%20a%20massive%20hit%2C%20earning%20over%20Rs%20600%20crores%20in%20India%20and%20nearing%20the%20Rs%201%2C100-crore%20mark%20globally.%20Filmmaker%20Anurag%20Kashyap%20expressed%20his%20happiness%20for%20Shah%20Rukh%20