ition%20parties%2C%20condemning%20the%20raids%20on%20journalists%20connected%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20have%20said%20that%20over%20the%20past%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberately%20persecuted%20and%20suppressed%E2%80%9D%20media%20organisations%20that%20speak%20truth%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20alliance%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfresh%20attack%20on%20the%20media%E2%80%9D%20compromises%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20standing%20as%20a%20mature%20democracy.%20%E2%80%9CIronically%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20paralysed%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20action%20against%20those%20journalists%20inciting%20hatred%20and%20divisiveness%20in%20the%20nation.%20In%20the%20national%20interest%2C%20it%20would%20behove%20the%20BJP%20Government%20to%20focus%20on%20genuine%20issues%20of%20concern%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20people%2C%20and%20stop%20attacking%20the%20media%20to%20distract%20attention%20from%20its%20failures%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20the%20Delhi%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdelhi-police-conducts-early-morning-raids-at-houses-of-journalists-satirists%5C%22%3Eraided%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20homes%20of%20several%20journalists%20and%20commentators%20associated%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20case%20under%20the%20draconian%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA).%20The%20case%20was%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20about%20an%20American%20millionaire%20who%20allegedly%20worked%20closely%20with%20the%20Chinese%20government%20to%20finance%20its%20propaganda%20worldwide.%20Subsequently%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-nishikant-dubey-rahul-gandhi-newsclick-independent-journalists-chinese-links-nyt-repor