s%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20place%20of%20birth%2C%20residence%2C%20language%2C%20etc.%2C%20and%20doing%20acts%20prejudicial%20to%20maintenance%20of%20harmony)%20and%20120%20(b)%20(party%20to%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20other%20than%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20an%20offence)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20purportedly%20has%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20claim%2C%20citing%20a%20NYT%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fneville-roy-singham-china-propaganda.html%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20Congress%20leaders%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0had%20received%20funds%20from%20China%20to%20create%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-India%E2%80%9D%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERaided%20employees%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%C2%A0were%20asked%20about%20whether%20they%20had%20reported%20on%20events%20like%20the%20farmers%20protest%20and%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20has%20released%20a%20statement%20strongly%20condemning%20the%20raids%20and%20noting%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Csteadfastly%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20media%20and%20for%20constitutionally-protected%20freedoms%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20noted%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20particular%20role%20vis-a-vis%20the%20media%2C%20mentioning%20the%20crushing%20effects%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20deliberately%20persecuted%20and%20suppressed%20the%20media%20by%20deploying%20investigative%20agencies%20to%20suppress%20the%20British%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%2C%20Newslaundry%2C%20Dainik%20Bhaskar%2C%20Bharat%20Samachar%2C%20the%20Kashmir%20Walla%2C%20The%20Wire%20etc.%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20the%20journalists%20of%20NewsClick.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20government%20has%20also%20tried%20to%20convert%20the%20media%20into%20a%20mouthpiece%20for%20its%20partisan%20and%20ideological%20interests%20by%20facilitating%20the%20takeover%20of%20media%20organisations%20by%20crony%20capitalists.%20Both%20the%20government%20and%20its%20ideologically%20aligned%20organisations%20have%20resorted%20to%20reprisals%20against%20individual%20journalists%20who%20spoke%20truth%20to%20power.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20also%20spearheaded%20regressive%20policies%20like%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Rules%202021%20that%20constrict%20the%20media%20from%20reporting%20objectively.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20only%20hiding%20its%20sins%20of%20omissions%20and%20commission%20from%20the%20people%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20also%20compromising%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20standing%20as%20a%20mature%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20observed%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20coercive%20actions%20are%20%E2%80%9Cinvariably%20directed%20against%20only%20those%20media%20organisations%20and%20journalists%20that%20speak%20truth%20to%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20mention%20of%20hate%20speech%20on%20news%20platforms%20being%20given%20the%20miss.%20%E2%80%9CIronically%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20paralysed%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20taking%20action%20against%20those%20journalists%20inciting%20hatred%20and%20divisiveness%20in%20the%20nation.%20In%20the%20national%20interest%2C%20it%20would%20behove%20the%20BJP%20Government%20to%20focus%20on%20genuine%20issues%20of%20concern%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20people%2C%20and%20stop%20attacking%20the%20media%20to%20distract%20attention%20from%20its%20failures%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Distraction%20tactic%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20Pawan%20Kh