ructionist%20violence%20against%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%2C%20none%20is%20as%20reprehensible%20and%20shocking%20as%20the%20massacre%20at%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20comprehensive%2C%20fact-finding%20report%2C%20%3Cem%3ETekunia%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20Massacre%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20democratic%20rights%20activists%20from%20several%20organisations%20highlight%20details%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20socio-economic%20background%20of%20the%20region%2C%20and%20its%20political%20culture.%20What%20stands%20out%20are%20three%20key%20dimensions%20%E2%80%93%20the%20unresolved%20agrarian%20questions%2C%20the%20distortions%20of%20democracy%2C%20and%20the%20culture%20of%20impunity%20%E2%80%93%20which%20coalesce%20to%20render%20our%20democratic%20apparatus%2C%20its%20structures%2C%20processes%2C%20and%20culture%20ineffective%20against%20the%20rising%20tide%20of%20%E2%80%98electoral%20authoritarianism%E2%80%99%20in%20which%20violence%20against%20innocent%20citizens%20is%20legitimised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnresolved%20land%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20authors%20detail%20about%20the%20region%20that%20is%20underdeveloped%20economically%20and%20socially%20(with%20all%20its%20socio-economic%20parameters%20below%20the%20national%20average)%20also%20encapsulates%20the%20fall-out%20of%20the%20unresolved%20land%20questions.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20ecologically%20rich%20Tarai%20region%2C%20in%20which%20Sikh%20farmers%20were%20encouraged%20to%20settle%20and%20render%20productive%2C%20there%20are%20now%20economic%20and%20political%20tensions%20as%20to%20who%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98outsider%E2%80%99%20and%20who%20the%20%E2%80%98insider%E2%80%99.%20That%20such%20a%20region%20manifests%20all%20the%20key%20features%20of%20agrarian%20distress%20(over-indebted%20farmers%2C%20inadequate%20farm%20incomes%2C%20exhausted%20lands%2C%20etc.)%20also%20highlights%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20current%20dominant%20model%20of%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20farmers%20who%20had%20gathered%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20massacre%20were%20supporters%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20led%20by%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%2C%20and%20were%20seeking%20solutions%20to%20the%20myriad%20problems%20that%20they%20faced%20and%20which%20would%20have%20been%20exacerbated%20with%20the%20now-repealed%20three%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Flakhimpur-kheri-violence-was-a-long-time-coming%5C%22%3EThe%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20Incident%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Occur%20by%20Chance%2C%20it%20Was%20a%20Long%20Time%20Coming%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDistortions%20of%20democracy%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20dimension%20that%20the%20report%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20is%20that%20of%20the%20distortions%20of%20democracy%20which%20have%20been%20built%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20as%20a%20nation%20we%20have%20consolidated%20what%20Ambedkar%20cautioned%20against%3A%20the%20deployment%20of%20an%20electoral%20or%20political%20democracy%20without%20the%20indispensable%20and%20important%20economic%20democracy.%20That%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%2C%20Ajay%20Mishra%20or%20%E2%80%98Teni%E2%80%99%2C%20holds%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ejanta%20adalat%20%3C%2Fem%3E(people%E2%80%99s%20court)%E2%80%9D%20at%20his%20house%2C%20and%20is%20the%20local%2C%20wealthy%20patron%20who%20has%20been%20elected%20by%20impoverished%20rural%20citizens%20indicates%20how%20a%20%E2%80%98patron-client%E2%80%99%20culture%20constitutes%20the%20foundation%20on%20which%20patronage%20and%20pelf%2C%20protection%20and%20exploitation%20form%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20coin%20of%20our%20rural%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F11174825%2F2021_10img09_Oct_2021_PTI10_09_2021_000153B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F11174825%2F2021_10img09_Oct_2021_PTI10_09_2021_000153B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F11174825%2F2021_10img09_Oct_2021_PTI10_09_2021_000153B-300x234.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F11174825%2F2021_10img09_Oct_2021_PTI10_09_2021_000153B-1024x797.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-557665%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22934%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndian%20Youth%20Congress%20members%20shout%20slogans%20during%20a%20protest%20demanding%20the%20immediate%20arrest%20of%20Ashish%20Mishra%2C%20accused%20in%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20violence%2C%20near%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20October%209%2C%202021.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%2FKamal%20Singh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ECombining%20muscle%20power%20with%20legal%20and%20illegal%20political%20and%20economic%20transactions%2C%20elected%20leaders%20ride%20on%20predatory%20capitalism%20to%20co-opt%20customary%20institutions%20and%20transactions.%20That%20the%20regional%20sport%20form%20of%20wrestling%20or%20%3Cem%3Edangel%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20once%20a%20community-based%20physical%20prowess%20that%20was%20a%20form%20of%20recognition%20and%20entertainment%20for%20a%20rural%20culture%2C%20is%20now%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20organising%20strength%20of%20politicians%20indicates%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20such%20collective%20and%20community%20activities%20have%20been%20subverted%20and%20subordinated%20to%20become%20sites%20and%20processes%20for%20political%20big-manship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAjay%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20rise%20and%20rise%20to%20unlimited%20power%20resulted%20from%20such%20a%20configuration.%20The%20report%20provides%20a%20summative%20portrait%20of%20the%20man%3A%20a%20bully%20who%20posed%20as%20an%20arbitrator%20of%20justice%2C%20primarily%20because%20democracy%E2%80%99s%20own%20institutions%20especially%20that%20of%20the%20police%20and%20judiciary%20are%20out%20of%20reach%20of%20the%20average%20citizen%2C%20whose%20wealth%20grew%20unbounded%20into%20multiple%20crores%2C%20who%20flaunted%20the%20symbols%20of%20power%20and%20status%20(including%20expensive%20cars)%2C%20and%20who%20was%20repeatedly%20elected%20despite%20a%20record%20that%20shows%20no%20contribution%20to%20his%20constituency%2C%20and%20whose%20son%20had%20aspirations%20to%20contest%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fact-finding%20report%20reproduces%20a%20photograph%20of%20the%20primary%20health%20centre%20at%20Tikunia%2C%20a%20neglected%20set%20of%20buildings%20amidst%20slush%2C%20weeds%20and%20waste.%20That%20this%20is%20the%20state%20of%20a%20health%20centre%20during%20the%20ongoing%20COVID-19%20epidemic%20speaks%20volumes%20for%20the%20state%20of%20underdevelopment%20in%20the%20region.%20Such%20distortions%20of%20democracy%20have%20also%20laid%20the%20foundations%20for%20a%20culture%20of%20impunity%20in%20which%20gross%20criminal%20and%20civil%20violations%20are%20not%20made%20accountable%20to%20the%20laws%20of%20the%20state%20or%20to%20the%20moral%20strictures%20of%20society.%20That%20Ajay%20Mishra%20is%20accused%20of%20murdering%20his%20political%20opponent%20in%20his%20very%20first%20election%20at%20the%20Zilla%20Panchayat%20level%2C%20but%20is%20able%20to%20be%20exonerated%20and%20then%20elected%20repeatedly%20to%20the%20parliament%20is%20a%20record%20of%20the%20travesty%20of%20not%20only%20justice%20but%20also%20that%20of%20humanity%20and%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Flakhimpur-kheri-bjp-ashish-mishra-rule-of-law%5C%22%3EIn%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20BJP%20Proves%20India%20Has%20No%20Rule%20of%20Law%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%2C%20Mishra%20was%20able%20to%20threaten%20farmers%20in%20public%20and%20then%2C%20despite%20clear%20evidence%20and%20a%20report%20by%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20that%20implicates%20him%20and%20his%20son%20(now%20out%20on%20bail)%20for%20the%20massacre%20at%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20continues%20to%20hold%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20offices%20in%20the%20nation%2C%20makes%20a%20mockery%20of%20not%20only%20our%20administrative%20system%20but%20also%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20disdain%20for%20any%20moral%20accountability%20to%20its%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20massacre%20will%20be%20a%20litmus%20test%20case%20for%20the%20judiciary%20to%20deliver%20justice%20and%20for%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20organisations%20to%20persist%20in%20their%20assertion%20for%20justice.%20Its%20key%20learning%20will%20be%20that%20violence%20is%20now%20both%20a%20means%20and%20an%20end%20for%20political%20power%20and%20that%20the%20vehicle%20for%20such%20impunity%20is%20our%20compromised%20democracy%20and%20a%20culture%20of%20subordination%20among%20citizens.%20Even%20the%20state%20apparatus%20becomes%20an%20instrument%20of%20such%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20the%20report%20notes%2C%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20misinformation%20that%20the%20police%20provided%20to%20the%20farmers%2C%20the%20enforced%20cordoning%20of%20the%20protest%20site%20at%20Tikunia%20into%20a%20narrow%20strip%20that%20provided%20no%20escape%20for%20the%20speeding%2C%20killing%20vehicles%2C%20and%20the%20mystery%20of%20the%20death%20of%20one%20BJP%20worker%20who%20was%20alive%20when%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20police%20but%20was%20later%20found%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20planned%20massacre%20of%20innocents%20by%20powers%20that%20assumed%20they%20were%20beyond%20accountability%2C%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20will%20be%20the%20new%20ground%20in%20which%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement%20and%20their%20assertion%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20farmers%20and%20for%20democracy%20will%20stand%20to%20be%20tested.%20All%20kudos%20to%20the%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20for%20continuing%20to%20seek%20justice%20for%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20their%20perseverance%20be%20a%20way%20of%20asserting%20our%20democratic%20rights%20and%20of%20honouring%20the%20memories%20of%20all%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20massacre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERemembering%20farmers%20Nachattar%20Singh%2C%20Daljit%20Singh%2C%20Gurvinder%20Singh%2C%20and%20Lovepreet%20Singh%2C%20BJP%20workers%20Shyam%20Sundar%20Nishad%2C%20Hari%20Om%20Mishra%2C%20and%20Shubham%20Mishra%2C%20and%20journalist%3A%20Raman%20Kashyap.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA.R.%20Vaasavi%20is%20a%20social%20anthropologist%20based%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696301993000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F09111835%2F2021_10largeimg_1993082236.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftwo-years-after-lakhimpur-kheri-violence-three-issues-from-rural-india-that-cant-be-ignored%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fact-finding%20report%20published%20by%20rights%20activists%20points%20out%20that%20unresolved%20agrarian%20questions%2C%20distortions%20of%20democracy%2C%20and%20the%20culture%20of%20impunity%20in%20rural%20India%20are%20the%20reasons%20why%20such%20violence%20took%20place%20in%20the%20UP%20town.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ftwo-years-after-lakhimpur-kheri-violence-three-issues-from-rural-india-that-cant-be-ignored%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Police%20Conducts%20Early%20Morning%20Raids%20at%20Houses%20of%20Journalists%2C%20Satirists%2C%20Activists%22%2C%22cont