has%20been%20approved.%20Other%20patients%20are%20being%20treated%20as%20necessary%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dean%20also%20said%20that%20due%20to%20some%20staff%20members%20being%20posted%20out%20of%20the%20hospital.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20faced%20some%20difficulty%20since%20various%20staff%20were%20being%20transferred%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%2012%20adults%20who%20died%2C%20four%20have%20died%20due%20to%20heart%20attack%2C%20and%20others%20have%20died%20due%20to%20accidental%20injuries%2C%20complications%20during%20delivery%20and%20kidney%20failure%20among%20other%20complications.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20have%20launched%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20government%20demanding%20answers%20on%20these%20deaths.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20medical%20facilities%20and%20staff.%20Many%20nurses%20were%20transferred%20and%20their%20replacements%20were%20not%20given.%20Many%20machines%20are%20not%20working.%20The%20hospital%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20is%20500%2C%20but%201%2C200%20patients%20are%20admitted%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.freepressjournal.in%2Fmumbai%2Fmaharashtra-12-infants-among-24-dead-in-nanded-govt-hospital-in-past-24-hours-dean-cites-medicine-staff-shortage%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFree%20Press%20Journal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20former%20state%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20speak%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar%20(about%20this).%20The%20government%20should%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20keenly%20and%20take%20control%20of%20the%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Congress%20leader%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20told%20the%20media%20that%20several%20important%20machines