org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fauto-workers-union-expands-strike_n_6516dc78e4b0acbe63fa7b26%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fauto-workers-union-expands-strike_n_6516dc78e4b0acbe63fa7b26%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Forgotten%20Trailblazer%20Who%20First%20Introduced%20The%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ENari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20Adhiniyam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Parliament%20last%20week%2C%20under%20which%2C%2033%20percent%20of%20seats%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%20are%20promised%20to%20women.%20This%20landmark%20bill%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20454-2%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%20tabled%20in%201996%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20pending%20legislations%20in%20Parliament.%20It%20took%20eight%20different%20governments%2C%2027%20years%2C%20and%20a%20fight%20by%20women%20across%20the%20country%20to%20make%20this%20Bill%20a%20reality.%20Presently%2C%20there%20are%20102%20women%20parliamentarians%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20766%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20only%2013%20percent.%20This%20Bill%20is%20much%20needed%2C%20as%20India%20ranks%20141%20in%20women%20representation%20in%20parliament%2C%20as%20per%20an%20Inter-Parliamentary%20Union%20(IPU)%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20historic%20bill%20is%20here%20today%20thanks%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20many%20women%20politicians%20and%20activists%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328785%2Fimportant-letters-from-nehru-gandhi-sigmund-freud-that-shaped-india-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPramila%20Dandavate%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20MP%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20who%20had%20first%20introduced%20this%20Bill%20as%20a%20private%20member%