about%20the%20choice%20of%20working%20with%20scrap%20leather%20and%20why%20their%20brand%20went%20ahead%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20worked%20with%20scrap%20leather%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20people%20questioned%20our%20choice%20of%20material.%20They%20asked%20us%20why%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20use%20more%20vegan%20materials.%20We%20do%20not%20endorse%20the%20use%20of%20leather%20but%20scraps%20(waste)%20exist.%20Even%20with%20new-age%20materials%20like%20cork%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20overlook%20the%20aspect%20of%20scraps%20being%20present%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20harming%20the%20environment%20as%20well.%20Our%20work%20is%20to%20upcycle%20these%20scrap%20materials%20and%20eradicate%20waste%20that%20ends%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Gouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20scrap%20leather%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20started%20reinventing%20surface%20embellishments%20and%20techniques%20to%20find%20ways%20of%20upcycling%20this%20waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20luxury%20fashion%20out%20of%20waste%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-an