block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainable%20%26amp%3B%20sock-free%20shoes%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20research%20and%20development%20process%20of%20two%20years%2C%20the%20siblings%20found%20a%20sustainable%20alternative%20to%20manufacture%20environment-friendly%20shoes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSugarcane%20is%20widely%20used%20in%20India.%20When%20we%20drink%20%3Cem%3Eganne%20ka%20juice%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sugarcane%20juice)%2C%20we%20see%20the%20slag%20left%20behind%20as%20residue.%20Being%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20field%2C%20I%20came%20across%20Brazilian%20resin%20supplier%20which%20innovated%20sugarcane%20EVA%20(ethylene%20vinyl%20acetate)%20copolymer%20derived%20from%20sugarcane%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Parth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20to%20utilise%20the%20innovative%20carbon-negative%20material%2C%20Parth%20collaborated%20with%20the%20company%20to%20use%20sugarcane%20EVA%20to%20make%20the%20shoes%E2%80%99%20outsoles%20soft%20and%20comfortable.%20Other%20than%20this%2C%20they%20incorporated%20renewable%20and%20recyclable%20materials%20like%20merino%20wool%20and%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20to%203D-knit%20the%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20shoes%20are%20made%20from%20recycled%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20Parth%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20make%20pallets%20from%20plastic%20bottles%20which%20are%20then%20melted%20into%20yarn.%20We%20then%20blend%20merino%20wool%20into%20it%20to%20make%20propitiatory%20threads.%20So%2C%20while%20the%20outsoles%20made%20from%20sugarcane%20EVA%20provide%20durability%20and%20flexibility%20to%20the%20shoe%2C%20yarns%20made%20from%20single-use%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20merino%20wool%20with%20its%20natural%20antibacterial%20properties%20provide%20comfort%20for%20long-day%20use.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F